{"tid":1639833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女仔夜晚冇人唔好再着黑衫出街！","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T18:05:39.000Z","uid":211900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"861606d96e4c746d7064be468a1c173349152829","tid":1639833,"uid":211900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"當我求下你<br />\n人多或者日頭先好出嚟唱歌痴牆<br />\n示威遊行開花有猛男保護先至發夢唔好白白犧牲！<br />\n唔想再見到有女仔俾人姦殺！<br />\n唔想再見到有𡃁仔𡃁妹俾人夾硬捉上車<br />\n仲有最後八日班警察就要跪低 <br />\n係呢八日之內一個都不能少 齊上齊落<br />\n男仔唔夠多人唔係大隻嘅話都唔好自己幾個人出去！<br />\n係深宵時分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgTrjkc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgTrjkc.png&h=3e03ecf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee7819631ad66e1b401d661e763ff26c03a483ec","tid":1639833,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"全世界無論男仔女仔都同我買防狼器<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639307</a>"},{"pid":"d8a8b5779de67a4111bdaecc2ee3c13ecf4c9a61","tid":1639833,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"屌 十足綁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5838217c8ea32df4da52fb2796df89778602dd","tid":1639833,"uid":283686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d52117fd1c055ca94e8e85c6abee401957ccf7","tid":1639833,"uid":211900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:05:39.000Z","msg":"而家個班狗賊專出黎捉啲15 6歲嘅女仔<br />\n冇大隻猛男保護 又跑得唔夠快嘅女仔<br />\n夜晚人小就唔好出嚟啦<br />\n出嚟至少都幾百個人嗰啲場面先至好出嚟 <br />\n幾十人嘅話唔夠打<br />\n如果唔對路嘅話走咗先保命重要啲<br />\n沒有分化成份 自己判斷 覺得戰鬥力唔多夠嘅話<br />\n情勢唔對路走先！"}]}